title: Rom The Spaceknight (New Scans)
description:
Rom Spaceknight was a comic book series published by Marvel Comics and was set in Marvel&#039;s shared universe (known as the Marvel Universe). The comic book character Rom first appeared in Rom #1 (1979) and was created by Bill Mantlo and Al Milgrom. 

This torrent contains new scans of issues 1-50 by Tklemme. I have replaced my original Rom comics with this one. The scans are really good and must for every Rom fan. 

Enjoy and Seed.
